# Lyberty - AI Engine for Builders

## Project Overview

Lyberty is a comprehensive AI engine platform built as a monorepo with multiple applications and services. The project uses modern technologies including Next.js 15, Tauri, Rust, and Cloudflare infrastructure.

## Core Architecture

- **Frontend**: Next.js 15 with App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS with custom design system
- **State Management**: Jotai for global state management
- **Database**: Drizzle ORM with PostgreSQL for time-series metrics storage
- **Authentication**: Auth.js with multiple providers
- **Deployment**: Cloudflare Pages for web apps, Tauri for desktop/iOS
- **Monorepo**: Turborepo with pnpm workspaces

## App Structure

### Marketing Site (apps/marketing)

- **Purpose**: SEO, lead generation, marketing presence
- **Features**: Full Next.js 15 capabilities (edge middleware, server components, image optimization)
- **Deployment**: Cloudflare Pages with full edge features
- **URL**: lyberty.ai

### Main Web App (apps/web)

- **Purpose**: Main product application
- **Features**: Static export for Tauri desktop/iOS wrapping
- **Deployment**: Cloudflare Pages (static export)
- **URL**: app.lyberty.ai (future)

### Desktop/iOS Apps

- **Purpose**: Native wrappers around the main web app
- **Features**: Tauri desktop and iOS applications
- **Distribution**: App stores, direct downloads

